INSERT INTO UNIQUEID (TABLENAME, NEXTID) VALUES ('UserName
', 100)


Steps to migrating existing VARS databases:
  1. Create a copy of your original database tables
  2. Copy KB from original to new
  3. Run VARS-REDUX schema upgrade script on the new databas
  4. Increment all values in UniqueID table by 1
  5. Set LAST_UPDATE_TIME values to some date (instead of null)
  6. remove all rowguid columns and there associated index
  7. Modify annotation view by dropping reference to Association_Child_Parent table @done

	